<HEAD>With PM-Poll-Christmas, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 This <ORGANIZATION> Media </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> General-Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> poll is based on telephone interviews conducted Nov. 10-20 with 1,084 adults in the continental <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION>. The phone numbers were selected randomly by computer, and interviews were conducted with the adult who had the most recent birthday. The results were weighted to adjust for variations in the sample. The poll has a 3 percentage-point margin of error, meaning that if every adult American were asked the same questions, the results theoretically would be within 3 points of the poll's results, 19 of 20 times. The error margin is larger for subgroups _ 5 points, for example, for Southerners. Other sources of potential error in polls include the wording and order of questions. The questions and responses in this poll follow; because of rounding, sums may not total 100: 1. Do you celebrate Christmas? Yes: 96 percent. No: 5 percent. 2. Are the Christmas holidays something you look forward to, or not? Yes: 87. No: 13. Do n't know-no answer: 1. 3. Do you think of Christmas more as a religious occasion, or a family and social occasion? Religious: 26. Family, social: 34. Both: 38. Neither: 1. DK-NA: 1. 4. Do you think Christmas is too commercialized? Yes: 85. No: 14. DK-NA: 2. 5. How many people will you be giving Christmas gifts to this year? None: 3. One-two: 2. Three-five: 8. Six-nine: 16. Ten-14: 28. Fifteen-20: 21. Twenty-plus: 20. DK-NA: 3. 6. Compared to the last few years, will you spend more money on gifts this Christmas season, or less money, or about the same amount? More: 27. Less: 23. Same: 48. DK-NA: 2. 7. Stop me when I get to the sum that you expect to spend on Christmas gifts this year: Less than $ 50: 3. $ 50 - $ 100: 7 $ 100 - $ 200: 18 $ 200 - $ 300: 19 $ 300 - $ 500: 22 More than $ 500: 26. DK-NA: 5. 8. Do you usually receive the gifts you really want for Christmas, or not? Yes: 70. No: 25. DK-NA: 5. 9. Generally, do you attend church services during the year? Yes: 69. No: 30. 9a. -LRB- If yes -RRB- have you been to church services within the past week? Yes: 61. No: 39. 9b. -LRB- If no -RRB- within the past month? Yes: 67. No: 33. 9c. -LRB- If no -RRB- within the past six months? Yes: 80. No: 19. DK-NA: 1. 10. Do you attend church services on Christmas? Yes: 64. No: 34. DK-NA: 2.
