<FIRST>a a BC-History Adv19   12-12 0472</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-History, Adv19,0492</SECOND>
<NOTE>$adv19</NOTE>
<NOTE>For Release Monday, Dec. 19</NOTE>
<HEAD>Today in History</HEAD>
<HEAD>By The Associated Press</HEAD>
