<FIRST>r f PM-BusinessHighlights 2Takes   12-12 0528</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Business Highlights, 2 Takes,0549</SECOND>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
